N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5013.4 - Prize funds

State Regulations

In the event of termination of the Quick Draw game for
any reason, any prize monies remaining may be used for prizes in other lottery
games at the discretion of the commission. Notes
